    <item>
      <title>日本的银行领先股票较低，收益率下降，因为Outlook Dearkens</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/japan-s-banks-lead-stocks-lower-yields-drop-as-outlook-darkens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股票跌倒，银行股票的下降幅度急剧下降，而下级政府债券收益率，因为美国的税率使美国的经济前景变黑，并推迟了对利率上涨的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/japan-s-banks-lead-stocks-lower-yields-drop-as-outlook-darkens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布吉的乌达（Ueda）引用特朗普的关税后，不确定性加剧了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/boj-s-ueda-aims-to-convey-continuity-after-tariffs-upend-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本银行州长Kazuo Ueda表示，美国关税增加了经济前景的不确定性，并将对增长进行权衡，这表明中央银行可能需要更多时间来评估唐纳德·特朗普在提高基准率之前的政策的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/boj-s-ueda-aims-to-convey-continuity-after-tariffs-upend-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚公司在特朗普关税后提出针对新税收的案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/malaysian-firms-make-case-against-new-taxes-post-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚制造商敦促政府避免在美国宣布向东南亚国家宣布24％的互惠关税后，今年不再引入额外的税收负担，理由是成本压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/malaysian-firms-make-case-against-new-taxes-post-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:35:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
