    <item>
      <title>自2020年以来，垃圾债券遭受了最糟糕的溃败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/global-junk-bonds-suffer-worst-rout-since-2020-as-traders-flee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2020年以来，美国垃圾公司的债券带领全球高级债务债务最大，这是一个世纪以来美国最陡峭的关税引发了人们对全球增长的恐惧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/global-junk-bonds-suffer-worst-rout-since-2020-as-traders-flee</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:40:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本的股票滑动，全球增长前景对关税的变化变黑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japanese-stocks-set-to-fall-as-global-rout-deepens-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税将降低世界经济的关注，日本股票下跌，全球投资者倾倒了风险更高的资产。如果我们征收经济税，而日元更大的日元损害出口公司，则银行股票在日本景观银行中最多的股票不会太多提高利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japanese-stocks-set-to-fall-as-global-rout-deepens-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票在全球溃败之后下跌，美元下降：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的最新关税措施将投资者推向天堂资产之后，亚洲股票在两个月内下降到了两个月的最低水平，扩大了全球股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
